narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned basic French grammar and vocabulary. By the end of the course, I had a small amount of conversational fluency.
I have gone from zero French knowledge to a modest level of proficiency in understanding written and some spoken French.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The immersive experience was definitely a strength of this course, however I would appreciate if the curriculum paid more attention to explaining relevant grammatical structures as they come up instead of just teaching students how to use the grammar in practice.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! Learning French has been incredibly rewarding - this was my best class this semester. This course has inspired me to continue studying French and to begin a second foreign language.
